{"id":597347,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/【立此存照】新时代铁拳：戏唱国歌账号被封/","date":"2018-10-10T08:28:58Z","modified":"2018-10-15T08:30:28Z","title":"【立此存照】新时代铁拳：“戏唱国歌”账号被封","content":"<p>近日，虎牙主播@莉哥OvO 在直播中，“篡改国歌曲谱，以嬉皮笑脸的方式表现国歌内容”（官媒原文），将其作为自己的“莉猪音乐会第一期”的“开幕曲”，目前直播间已被虎牙封禁。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/50fd482dly1fw2ue8xgvsj20c809ewes.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-597353\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/50fd482dly1fw2ue8xgvsj20c809ewes.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"338\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/50fd482dly1fw2ue8xgvsj20c809ewes.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/50fd482dly1fw2ue8xgvsj20c809ewes-300x230.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌2.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-597360\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌2.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"280\" height=\"209\" /></a></p>\n<p>视频<a href=\"https://weibo.com/tv/v/jFcwfQuWA?fid=1034:4293542408076250\">地址</a></p>\n<p>杨凯莉本人深夜致歉，称自己行为低级且愚蠢，但平台尚未对此事做出回应。（来源：凤凰网视频）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340499FNbBV.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-597354\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340499FNbBV.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"550\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340499FNbBV.png 589w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340499FNbBV-273x300.png 273w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p>在虎牙直播的官方声明中称，对于 @莉哥OvO 的处罚包括：1.封禁直播间。2.冻结直播账号。3.下架全部作品。4.对其进行整改教育。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340503THOba.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-597355\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340503THOba.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"345\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340503THOba.png 610w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/15391340503THOba-300x207.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>中共网警提醒，根据《中华人民共和国国歌法》，在公共场合故意篡改国歌歌词、曲谱，以歪曲、 贬损方式奏唱国歌，或者以其他方式侮辱国歌的，由公安机关处以警告或者十五日以下拘留;构成犯罪的，依法追究刑事责任。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-597359\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"440\" height=\"402\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2018/10/国歌-300x274.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 440px) 100vw, 440px\" /></a></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>中国数字时代此前曾报道，英雄联盟一解说因一句“一种黄继光的打法往你枪口上冲”遭事后处罚。目前中国国内娱乐直播界文字狱频发，在新时代以前完全无法想象的事情，都在真实地发生着。</p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote><p><a title=\"【立此存照】“用一种黄继光的打法往你枪口上冲”\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2018/10/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e7%94%a8%e4%b8%80%e7%a7%8d%e9%bb%84%e7%bb%a7%e5%85%89%e7%9a%84%e6%89%93%e6%b3%95%e5%be%80%e4%bd%a0%e6%9e%aa%e5%8f%a3%e4%b8%8a%e5%86%b2/\">【立此存照】“用一种黄继光的打法往你枪口上冲”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[29060,34679,27697,32935,36489,34718,21170,33267,9375,36426,34885,36427,36428,34654,17010]}